.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, mirinda, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, drawing, singing, writing
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, artichoke, garlic, watermelon
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, hamster, mouse
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, subway, trike, van
 1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
 2. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person eating cranberry##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 5. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
 7. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 8. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is the person driving the subway##1
10. the person drinking water is the owner of the dog##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Beverage    | coffee     | hot-chocolate  | water       | mirinda      |
| Hobby       | singing    | writing        | collecting  | drawing      |
| Food         | artichoke  | watermelon | cranberry | garlic |
| Pet         | chinchilla | mouse          | dog         | hamster      |
| Transport   | subway     | helicopter     | trike       | van          |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, sprite, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, magic-tricks, video-games, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller, western
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, british, indonesian, mexican
4 different games are played: whist, backgammon, snooker, monopoly
 1. the indonesian is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is the person watching western movies##1
 3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 4. the mexican is on the left of the brazilian##1
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person drinking water##1
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 8. the brazilian is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is the person watching thriller movies##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
11. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | water       | sprite      | mirinda      | juice    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | video-games | magic-tricks | dancing  |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller    | mystery     | western      | disaster |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | mexican     | brazilian    | british  |
| Game           | backgammon  | monopoly       | whist          | snooker      |

